text:
Kissena Boulevard, east side, between Fifty-ninth Ave., and Horace Harding Boulevard, showing the James Fogarty house which has been in this family since 1873. Eugene L. Armbruster believes it to be a remodelled 18th Century house; it was again remodelled in 1924. C. Cornwall was the owner in 1860.

January 1923.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
